  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class VisibleRecipientChip
extends android.text.style.ImageSpan
implements DrawableRecipientChip
    VisibleRecipientChip defines an ImageSpan that contains information relevant to a particular recipient and renders a background asset to go with it.
